        <Parent_String>stilettos (daggers) [300037073], daggers (weapons) [300037058], edged weapons [300036973], armaments [300420324], weapons [300036926], Weapons and Ammunition (hierarchy name) [300036743], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
